DermIntel: Personalized Ingredient Analyzer
DermIntel is an intelligent web application designed to demystify cosmetic ingredient labels and provide personalized, skin-type-aware suitability analyses and product recommendations. By translating complex scientific names into plain language and mapping them directly to a user's unique skin profile, DermIntel helps consumers make safe, healthy, and cost-effective beauty decisions.

The Founder's Pitch & Product Vision
Every day, millions of people stand in front of store shelves or scroll through e-commerce apps looking at product labels containing words like Niacinamide, Phenoxyethanol, or Methylparaben. They have no idea what these chemicals do, whether they are safe, or if they will cause an breakout or allergic reaction. They are buying blind, guided only by influencer hype and slick marketing.

DermIntel is here to change that. We are building the "Waze of skincare."

