Risk Penalty: High-risk ingredients deduct 15 points, medium-risk deduct 5 points.
Personalization Engine:
If user profile has skin_type == OILY, ingredients with comedogenic_rating >= 3 trigger a high penalty (comedogenic alert).
If user profile has skin_type == SENSITIVE, ingredients with irritation_score >= 2 or marked as fragrance/essential oils trigger suitability penalties.
If user profile has skin_concerns containing ACNE, ingredients with anti-acne properties (Salicylic Acid, Zinc PCA) add positive boosts.
If user profile has skin_type == DRY, hydrating ingredients (Glycerin, Hyaluronic Acid) add positive boosts.
